                Firma Auga<lb break="no" n="2"/>ntian<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> <note>sic</note> fili<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> ti<lb break="no" n="3"/>tulum posui<lb break="no" n="4"/>t qu<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>e</abbr></expan> vixit a<lb break="no" n="5"/>nnis XXIIII <expan><abbr>d</abbr><ex>iebus</ex></expan> V </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>anibus</ex></expan>
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Hedera in Z. 1. Z. 6 befindet sich auf dem Rahmen; Buchstabe M mit zusätzlicher abfallender Schräghaste am Anfang. (B): EphEp; NSA 1886: Z. 3/4: posu[i]/t.</p>
